    "chunk_index": 0,
    "chunk_text": "A dict from the previous example. In the previous example, we were returning a dict from our dependency (\"dependable\"): But then we get a dict in the parameter commons of the path operation function . And we know that editors can't provide a lot of support (like completion) for dict s, because they can't know their keys and value types. We can do better...",
